findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply() may abort with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges, including initializing the contract, changing bridge addresses, opening trading, modifying maxTxAmount, pausing/unpausing the contract, excluding from fees, and changing marketing wallets and fee rates.
